<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٨١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُّدْهِنُونَ}</span> ... مُكَذِّبُونَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٨٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَتَجْعَلُونَ رِزْقَكُمْ}</span> ... تَجْعَلُونَ شُكْرَ نِعَمِ اللهِ عَلَيْكُمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٨٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَلَغَتِ الْحُلْقُومَ}</span> ... وَصَلَتِ الرُّوحُ الحُلْقُومَ عِنْدَ المَوْتِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٨٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غَيْرَ مَدِينِينَ}</span> ... غَيْرَ مَجْزِيِّينَ، وَمُحَاسَبِينَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٨٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَرْجِعُونَهَا}</span> ... تَرُدُّونَ الرُّوحَ إِلَى الجَسَدِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٨٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَرَوْحٌ}</span> ... رَحْمَةٌ وَاسِعَةٌ، وَاسْتِرَاحَةٌ، وَفَرَحٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَرَيْحَانٌ}</span> ... رِزْقٌ حَسَنٌ، وَرَائِحَةٌ طَيِّبَةٌ، وَجَمِيعُ مَا تَطِيبُ بِهِ نَفْسُهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٩١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَسَلَامٌ لَّكَ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> يُقَالُ لَهُ:</span> سَلَامَةٌ لَكَ، وَأَمْنٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٩١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِنْ أَصْحَابِ الْيَمِينِ}</span> ... لِكَوْنِكَ مِنْ أَصْحَابِ اليَمِينِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٩٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَنُزُلٌ}</span> ... ضِيَافَةٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٩٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَمِيمٍ}</span> ... شَرَابِ جَهَنَّمَ المُتَنَاهِي فِي الحَرَارَةِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٩٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَتَصْلِيَةُ جَحِيمٍ}</span> ... يَدْخُلُ فِيهَا، وَيُقَاسِي حَرَّهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٩٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَقُّ الْيَقِينِ}</span> ... لَا مِرْيَةَ فِيهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>